file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: wallet web app demo
  version: '1.1'
servers:
  - url: 'http://localhost:3000'
paths:
  '/wallets/{walletName}':
    parameters:
      - schema:
          type: string
        name: walletName
        in: path
        required: true
    get:
      summary: get wallet info
      tags: []
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/wallet'
              examples: {}
      operationId: get-wallets-walletName
      description: get wallet object
  '/wallets/{walletName}/tokens':
    parameters:
      - schema:
          type: string
        name: walletName
        in: path
        required: true
    get:
      summary: get token list in wallet
      tags: []
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          headers: {}
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                description: ''
                type: object
                properties:
                  tokens:
                    type: array
                    uniqueItems: true
                    minItems: 1
                    items:
                      required:
                        - id
                        - capture_id
                        - capture_photo_url
                        - created_at
                        - planter_id
                        - planter_name
                        - planter_photo_url
                      properties:
                        id:
                          type: string
                          minLength: 1
                        capture_id:
                          type: string
                          minLength: 1
                        capture_photo_url:
                          type: string
                          minLength: 1
                        created_at:
                          type: string
                          minLength: 1
                        planter_id:
                          type: string
                          minLength: 1
                        planter_name:
                          type: string
                          minLength: 1
                        planter_photo_url:
                          type: string
                          minLength: 1
                required:
                  - tokens
                x-examples:
                  example-1:
                    tokens:
                      - id: c488301f-1117-48c3-8866-3c38f28d3f25
                        capture_id: '932758'
                        capture_photo_url: 'https://treetracker-production-images.s3.eu-central-1.amazonaws.com/2021.05.19.09.42.48_-4.882362633999999_38.38042393_e930d565-e28c-4e28-a313-16c85df989f1_IMG_20210517_143630_167714448.jpg'

  '/tokens/{tokenId}/transactions':
    parameters:
      - schema:
          type: string
        name: tokenId
        in: path
        required: true
    get:
      summary: Your GET endpoint
      tags: []
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                description: ''
                type: object
                properties:
                  transactions:
                    type: array
                    uniqueItems: true
                    minItems: 1
                    items:
                      required:

                        - sender_wallet_id
                        - sender_wallet_name

                        sender_wallet_id:

                        sender_wallet_name:

                        receiver_wallet_id:

                        receiver_wallet_name:
                          type: string
                          minLength: 1
                        created_at:
                          type: string

                required:

                x-examples:

                    transactions:

                        sender_wallet_name: Stephanie
                        receiver_wallet_id: b4f97ada-1468-11ec-82a8-0242ac130003

                        created_at: '5/19/2021, 9:21:11 PM'
              examples:
                example-transaction:
                  value:
                    transactions:
                      - id: 43ad1a4e-1468-11ec-82a8-0242ac130003
                        sender_wallet_id: 4f4a4426-1468-11ec-82a8-0242ac130003
                        sender_wallet_name: Zaven
                        receiver_wallet_id: 5e1e4ab0-1468-11ec-82a8-0242ac130003
